lt="" width="300" height="225" /></a>\r\n\r\n</div>', '冬', '冬天到了。其实冬天早就到了。', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '113-revision-17', '', '', '2012-12-09 13:29:57', '2012-12-09 05:29:57', '', 113, 'https://umbrella.im/113-revision-17', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
